  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Invoicing gives your company tools to manage customers and corporate clients with net terms. Invoicing is available to users on our Advanced and Professional plans.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934196827/Invoice%201.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"InvoicingResources-BenefitsofInvoicing\">Benefits of Invoicing</h2><ul><li><p>Keep track of corporate relationships\u00a0\u2014 repairs, warranties, and payment terms.</p></li><li><p>Negotiate net terms and discounts with corporate clients and apply those terms and discounts to issued invoices.</p></li><li><p>Expedite corporate transactions by tying customers to accounts and issuing invoices.\u00a0</p></li><li><p>Manage Accounts Receivable to ensure on-time payments.</p></li><li><p>View the balance of all tickets associated with an invoice and record payments of several tickets at once.</p></li><li><p>Manage discounts on corporate accounts, ensuring that corporate clients are getting the proper preferred rate for each ticket.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934196827/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"InvoicingResources-AdditionalResourcesandTutorials\">Additional Resources and Tutorials</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934327935/Invoicing+Creating+Billing+Agents\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934327935\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Creating Billing Agents</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934917701/Invoicing+Net+Terms+Billing+for+Customers\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934917701\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Net Terms Billing for Customers</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934196840/Invoicing+Creating+and+Managing+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934196840\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Creating and Managing Invoices</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229611/Invoicing+Editing+Tickets+on+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229611\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoices: Editing Tickets on Invoices</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934327961/Invoicing+Remittance+and+Reconciling+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934327961\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Remittance and Reconciling Invoices</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934917724/Invoicing+Refunding+and+Voiding+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934917724\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Refunding and Voiding Invoices</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934327948/Invoicing+Assigning+Billing+Agents+to+Customers+and+Tickets\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934327948\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Assigning Billing Agents to Customers and Tickets</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934360696/Invoicing+Managed+Services+Contract\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934360696\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Managed Services Contract</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934360682/Invoicing+Accepting+Advance+Payment+for+Net+Terms+Customers+and+Billing+Agents\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934360682\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Accepting Advance Payment for Net Terms Customers and Billing Agents</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934295142/Invoicing+Third-Party+Financing+Payment+Options+with+ACH+or+Check\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934295142\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Third-Party Financing Payment Options with ACH or Check</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934196854/Invoicing+Third-Party+Financing+Payment+Options+with+Virtual+Credit+Cards\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934196854\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Invoicing: Third-Party Financing Payment Options with Virtual Credit Cards</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934327922/Reports+Receivables+and+Invoice+Aging\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934327922\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Reports: Receivables and Invoice Aging</a></p><p /><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
